<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Orivraa Seller Network</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .wrapper { width: 100%; background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 40px 0; }
    .main { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #047857 100%); padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; }
    .content { padding: 40px; }
    .footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer p { margin: 5px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }
    .footer a { color: #10b981; text-decoration: none; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 20px 0; }
    p { margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #4b5563; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #047857 100%); color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .feature-list { margin: 30px 0; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
    .feature-list li { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .feature-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .feature-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 20px; }
    .feature-text { flex: 1; }
    .feature-text strong { display: block; color: #111827; font-size: 15px; }
    .feature-text span { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="main">
      <div class="header">
        <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="logo">🏪 {{appName}} Seller Network</a>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Welcome to {{appName}}, your new storefront! 🎉</h1>
        
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>Congratulations on opening your shop on {{appName}}! We are thrilled to have your jewelry business onboard, connecting you with eager customers worldwide.</p>
        
        <p>Here's what you can do from your new Seller Dashboard:</p>
        
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">💎</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Manage Your Inventory</strong>
              <span>Easily add, edit, and showcase your finest gold and silver pieces.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Reach Global Customers</strong>
              <span>Expand your business footprint beyond local borders.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Sales & Analytics</strong>
              <span>Track your performance, earnings, and trending items seamlessly.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">🤝</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Custom Requests (RFQs)</strong>
              <span>Receive and fulfill customized jewelry orders from customers.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Instant KYC & Trust</strong>
              <span>Complete your verification to get the 'Verified Seller' badge!</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard/shop" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
          Need help setting up your shop? Reply to this email or reach us at 
          <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #10b981;">{{supportEmail}}</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>Here's to a prosperous partnership! ✨</p>
        <p><strong>The {{appName}} Team</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>© {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p><a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard/shop/settings">Manage Your Shop</a> • <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">Contact Partner Support</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
